name: IFGPipeAttachmentSnapTargetInterface
comment: Interface for actors to implement to be a valid snap target for Pipeline attachments. Eg. PipelineSupports can implement this to allow pumps to snap directly to themselves

methods.name: IsValidSnapTargetForAttachment
methods.comment: Returns true if the passed in attachment class should snap to this target actor
